Subject: [patch 38/60] i2c: Fix NULL pointer dereference in i2c_new_probed_device
Content-Disposition: inline; filename=i2c-fix-null-pointer-dereference-in-i2c_new_probed_device.patch
Status: RO
Content-Length: 1254
